
[{"content":" 👋 Hi there 💻 关于本站 本站最初创建于2024年10月18日，主要用于预防某人想不起作者的联系方式（主要作用），也会随缘记录自己平时觉得有兴趣的东西，我的文笔不好，有的时候还会有错别字，文章有错误、有什么好的建议见解或者疑问的话十分欢迎通过邮箱或者其他方式告诉我。感谢🙏 📫 联系方式 你可以通过以下方式联系到我： ","date":"18 October 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/about/","section":"遇见のBlog","summary":"","title":"关于","type":"page"},{"content":"","date":"18 October 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/","section":"遇见のBlog","summary":"","title":"遇见のBlog","type":"page"},{"content":" 前言 不喜欢说话没有问题，做任何事情，都没有要求说必须是不沉默寡言的人。对，任何事情，甚至是主持人。\n那么关键是什么？是在正确的场合，说正确的话，这才是关键。\n如果需要一个人表达观点的时候，他唯唯诺诺，但是却推说自己是个沉默寡言的人，那么这个人大概率是个肚子里没货的人。\n能否合适合理合情的表达自己的观点，这点，可能只有你自己才能回答。\n音乐分享 Music: Fragile - DJ OKAWARI x Celeina Ann\n","date":"16 January 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/posts/02/","section":"Posts","summary":"","title":"”不喜欢说话“的人","type":"posts"},{"content":"","date":"16 January 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/tags/music/","section":"Tags","summary":"","title":"Music","type":"tags"},{"content":"","date":"16 January 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/tags/photo/","section":"Tags","summary":"","title":"Photo","type":"tags"},{"content":"","date":"16 January 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/posts/","section":"Posts","summary":"","title":"Posts","type":"posts"},{"content":"","date":"16 January 2024","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/tags/","section":"Tags","summary":"","title":"Tags","type":"tags"},{"content":" 前言 \u0026ldquo;快乐是个属于成年人的词儿。你不必问一个孩子他是否快乐，你能看得出来。成年人讨论快乐是因为他们大多都不快乐。\u0026rdquo; —— 珍妮特·温特森《橘子不是唯一的水果》\n音乐分享 Music: Nostalgia (Autumn Loves) - Otokaze\n","date":"23 December 2023","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/posts/03/","section":"Posts","summary":"","title":"快乐是属于成年人的词","type":"posts"},{"content":" 前言 生活真的难啊，不过都挺过来了，人都会慢慢长大，经历就像在黑屋子里面洗衣服，你不知道洗干净没有，只能一遍一遍的去洗，直到你走上战场的那一刻，灯亮了。你会发现，只要你认真洗过了，那件衣服就会光亮如新，而以后你每次在穿上这件衣服，你都会想起那段岁月。\n音乐分享 Music: Awaken - Nyte\n","date":"11 June 2023","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/posts/01/","section":"Posts","summary":"","title":"感到累时，证明正在走上坡路了","type":"posts"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/authors/","section":"Authors","summary":"","title":"Authors","type":"authors"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/categories/","section":"Categories","summary":"","title":"Categories","type":"categories"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/HEKELIE/HEKELIE.github.io/series/","section":"Series","summary":"","title":"Series","type":"series"}]